A vintage-style illustration of a traveler seated by an airplane window at night, bathed in soft amber reading light, deeply absorbed in a glowing tablet screen. The scene captures the cozy solitude of air travel, with clouds visible through the oval window and the warm glow of the device illuminating their face. Muted tones of deep blue, warm orange, and cream dominate the palette, with subtle grain texture reminiscent of 1960s travel posters. The composition emphasizes the intimate moment of digital reading during a journey, with elegant retro typography-inspired decorative borders framing the scene.
